summary: Born in Amsterdam but lived the majority of my life in Yaounde, Cameroon. Passion for entrepreneurship and everything technology-related. Likes to play padel and basketball any day of the week. A master's degree with a focus on Data Science. In search of the next opportunity to make a positive sustainable impact on the world around me.
